wikimedia-graph-tracking-category:
{{tracking category name}}
Name of the tracking category for pages with graphs, an old technology that is being phased out.
wikimedia-graph-tracking-category-desc: Description on [[Special:TrackingCategories]] for the {{msg-mw|wikimedia-graph-tracking-category}} tracking category.
wikimedia-graph-broken-category:
{{tracking category name}}
Name of the tracking category for pages with broken graphs. This is all pages with graphs on them, as the technology that is being phased out.
wikimedia-graph-broken-category-desc: Description on [[Special:TrackingCategories]] for the {{msg-mw|wikimedia-graph-broken-category}} tracking category.
wikimedia-graph-disabled:
{{Optional}}
This is a message that's shown on pages that have graphs on them, indicate that the graphs technology is disabled and being phased out.
wikimedia-graph-disabled-category:
{{tracking category name}}
Name of the tracking category for pages with disabled graphs. This is all pages with graphs on them, as the technology is no longer available.
wikimedia-graph-disabled-category-desc: Description on [[Special:TrackingCategories]] for the {{msg-mw|wikimedia-graph-disabled-category}} tracking category.
